caption:
Winter + resolutions can feel heavy, especially for healthcare workers who give so much already. 🫂

Remember: You’re not just caring for others - you deserve that same compassion too.

Swipe through for your gentle reminder that you’re already doing enough. No “new year, new you” pressure needed. 💜

👉 Share your favorite reminder below or tag a colleague who needs to hear this today. Sometimes we all need that little nudge to be kinder to ourselves.
